OL,3,CScotland's decision on assisted dying
OL,4,Ctakes pressure off England and Wales
OL,6,FHolyrood's decision on assisted dying
OL,7,Fisn't just of huge consequence for
OL,8,FScots ` a literal matter of life and
OL,9,Fdeath.
OL,11,FIt also has a significant impact on
OL,12,Fthe debate across the rest of the
OL,13,FBritish Isles.
OL,15,FUntil now, there seemed to be an
OL,16,Funrelenting momentum in favour of
OL,17,Flegalising assisted dying.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
