OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773857158
OL,3,CScotland's decision on assisted dying
OL,4,Ctakes pressure off England and Wales
OL,6,FFirst the Isle of Man passed a law,
OL,7,Fthen Jersey in the Channel Islands.
OL,8,FAnd last month Wales gave its consent
OL,9,Fto changing the law, though this was
OL,10,Fmore of a technical vote than an
OL,11,Fendorsement of assisted dying per se.
OL,13,FScotland could have continued that
OL,14,Ftrend, piling pressure on the House of
OL,15,FLords in Westminster, which currently
OL,16,Flooks as if it will block the Assisted
OL,17,FDying Bill for England and Wales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
