OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773857158
OL,3,CScotland's decision on assisted dying
OL,4,Ctakes pressure off England and Wales
OL,6,FThere have been raging constitutional
OL,7,Fdebates about whether it is fair for
OL,8,Fan unelected chamber to frustrate the
OL,9,Fwill of MPs, who passed the Assisted
OL,10,FDying Bill last summer.
OL,12,FWith over 1200 amendments proposed by
OL,13,Fpeers, the bill is due to run out of
OL,14,Ftime at the end of April. This week
OL,15,Fover 100 Labour MPs demanded that the
OL,16,FPrime Minister allow them time to
OL,17,Fresurrect it in the next session of
OL,18,FParliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
