PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773857158
OL,3,CScotland's decision on assisted dying
OL,4,Ctakes pressure off England and Wales
OL,6,FIf Holyrood ` again, an elected
OL,7,Fchamber ` had voted in favour of
OL,8,Fassisted dying, it could have framed
OL,9,Fthe debate as peers versus democracy.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
