PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773857158
OL,3,CScotland's decision on assisted dying
OL,4,Ctakes pressure off England and Wales
OL,6,FNo longer does the House of Lords look
OL,7,Fas if it is singularly holding back
OL,8,Fthe tide of change.
OL,10,FNow the Isle of Man and Jersey are
OL,11,Farguably the outliers within the
OL,12,FBritish Isles, though the lesson from
OL,13,Felsewhere in the world is that
OL,14,Fsupporters will keep on trying until
OL,15,Fthey do eventually change the law.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
